        <div class="content">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>
                Welcome to donateblood.Pk, Pakistan’s greatest blood donation
                website! Our platform is dedicated to connecting blood donors with
                people in need, imparting a lifeline of hope and guide to those
                requiring blood transfusions across the us of a country.
            </p>
            <div class="sub">
                Home /
                <a href="#"> About Us </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contain">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Together, We Can Save Lives and Build a Healthier World</h1>
            <p>
                At donateblood.pk, we believe in the transformative power of
                compassion and community. Our mission is simple yet profound: to
                connect generous donors with those in critical need, ensuring that
                every drop of blood contributes to saving lives and fostering a
                healthier future for all. Join us in this life-saving mission.
                Together, we can make a lasting impact—one donation at a time.
            </p>
        </div>
